  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The graceful creature within beats its soft wings against the egg, impatient to be hatched.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential to be a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">diligent</span> companion, scouting for resources from great heights.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一颗活生生的受精卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已可孵化！</span><br><br>此刻，寄宿在其中的优雅生物正轻轻拨动着自己的柔软翅膀，看来是迫不及待地想要出来了。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有特殊的基因潜质，如果好好培养，日后将会成为一位能够从高空侦查资源的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">勤勉</span>同伴。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>內部的優雅生物用柔軟翅膀拍動著蛋殼，等不及要孵化。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">勤奮</span>的同伴，能在高海拔搜索資源。"
  },
